<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel ahin lungkham chate,
 Sak, Thang, Sim leh Mala;
 Kimuh ni hin Lalpa Isu ei lawp in la,
 Lung kiguola na hehpihna chu gel khawmin;
 Khawvel kahna cheng hih mangin.

[V2]
 Na Thagauin ei hih dimin,
 Khawvel kah lai haiin;
 Hun lawp ungkau Aw Na hehpihte hin,
 Ma khan a hun deih puou;
 Aw lopi takin hung leng ta'n.

[V3]
 2. Ka hilh ka gen chim theihloh te,
 Na vanga lengkhawm in;
 Kalah thimthu a gen u maw Na thisan in,
 Muol tin leh tang tin gam tin apat hung khawmte;
 Aw leng inla pawl thiengtho in.

[V4]
 3. Zie lei hi vang lungkham kahna,
 Munin guot mah leh chin;
 Thagau Thiengtho lopi leh vangsakna lul chu,
 Mitin din pawm tak leh lunggil phatna hi hen;
 Aw Thagau Thiengtho hun pie'n la.

[V5]
 4. Aw Lal Isu, thawmhau takin,
 Keihaw ei umsak kin;
 Aw Nang vanga ngaih cheng len-guol a hung kim hin,
 Kumsawt a khawvel pak hawihna nunghei sanin;
 Mitin lunggil sungah chengin.</lyrics>
<title>Lungkham Chate</title>
<hymn_number>281</hymn_number>
<author>Lienvela</author>
</song>